BEAVER FEST MANAGMENT SYSTEM
BY: Hector Baeza & Eddie Dang
URL: http://classwork.engr.oregonstate.edu:4932 

1. OVERVIEW
The Beaver Fest Managment System is a web-based database management system designed 
to coordinate bands, venues, managers, and sponsors. The application allows 
administrators to schedule performances via a Many-to-Many relationship and 
manage festival logistics through a full suite of CRUD operations.

2. Tech Stack
Backend: Node.js / Express
Frontend: Handlebars (HBS), CSS3
Database: MySQL (MariaDB)
Dependencies: express, express-handlebars, mysql

